{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/Madness-Afloat-Steam-pagev2.png?t=1732262051\" />Set sail into the eerie and mystical waters of &quot;Madness Afloat&quot;, an <strong>action/adventure game</strong> where history, fantasy and cosmic horror collide. In an alternate 1899, steam power and ethereal energies have revolutionized naval warfare, creating a battleground like no other. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/EXPLORE@0.25x.png?t=1732262051\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/steam1.gif?t=1732262051\" />Navigate through an immersive world filled with <strong>historical fantasy</strong> and <strong>Lovecraftian dread</strong>, where every voyage plunges you deeper into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/UPGRADE@0.25x.png?t=1732262051\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/SteamGifs2.gif?t=1732262051\" />Along with your crew, your ship is of utmost importance. That's why it requires a special attention from you. Enhance both its <strong>visual and functional aspects</strong> along the way, <strong>improving your chances at survival</strong> and <strong>showing style</strong> while doing so!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/FIGHT@0.25x.png?t=1732262051\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/SteamGifs3.gif?t=1732262051\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight <strong>fast-paced battles</strong> against ships, structures and monsters. Do that either <strong>alone</strong> or <strong>together with your friends</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/CHOOSE_YOUR_CREW@0.25x.png?t=1732262051\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/extras/CharactersV4.png?t=1732262051\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a world full of <strong>interesting and colorful characters</strong>. Engage with them and potentially <strong>hire</strong> some of them into your crew. Each crew member brings their own <strong>specialized skills</strong> and <strong>special abilities</strong> into the fray, making <strong>crew management</strong> a critical aspect of gameplay, enabling you to combine them in different ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Summary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in an alternate-history setting rich with <strong>geopolitical tensions</strong> and <strong>ethereal mysteries</strong>. Explore <strong>dynamic environments</strong>, solve <strong>environmental puzzles</strong> and uncover the <strong>dark secrets of the ethereal seas</strong>.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3095020?t=1732262051","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3095020?t=1732262051","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732262051","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095020/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732262051","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2